      <section id="percentage-cgpa">
        <h2>Percentage to CGPA conversion</h2>
        <p>
          Some universities give percentages but you need CGPA for applications.
        </p>

        <h3>Using the CBSE formula (reverse)</h3>
        <div class="callout formula-callout">
          <strong>CGPA = Percentage ÷ 9.5</strong>
        </div>

        <div class="table-wrap">
